==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-aɪə|-aɪə]]

===Proper noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''Maya'''
# a member of a [[Mesoamerican]] [[civilization]] that existed in and around [[Mexico]] in the 4th to 10th centuries.
# a [[descendant]] of these people.
# any of the [[Mayan]] [[language]]s, such as [[Quiché]] and [[Yucatec]].
# a girl’s name.
# in Sanskrit God's creation both physical and metaphysical or alternatively magic and mystery

